drinking"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sleeping:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 541:) [and] as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalalN","text_ar":"طَلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated places:"},{"kind":"text","text":"one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^ayotu Talala","text_ar":"رَاَيْتُ طَلَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqaroyapi","text_ar":"القَرْيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I saw what was elevated of the land of the town,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"village."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 139.) ―         -b2-  And The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axoS","text_ar":"شَخْص"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bodily"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corporeal form"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"figure"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"substance, such as one sees from a distance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a thing, (Msb, K,) whatever it be; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalaAlapN","text_ar":"طَلَالَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl. of the former as above: (K:) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axoS","text_ar":"شَخْص"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a man; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalaAlapN","text_ar":"طَلَالَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O:) or, of a man, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"erect"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axoS","text_ar":"شَخْص"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juv~apN","text_ar":"جُثَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZalaAlapN","text_ar":"ظَلَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Z","text_ar":"ظ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies the same. (O and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zl","text_ar":"ظل"},{"kind":"text","text":".) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hay~aA A@ll~`hu Talalaka","text_ar":"حَيَّا ا@للّٰهُ طَلَلَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalaAlataka","text_ar":"طَلَالَتَكَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God preserve,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"save,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$axoS","text_ar":"شَخْص"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"person"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hay~aA A@ll~`hu","text_ar":"حَيَّا ا@للّٰهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talalaka","text_ar":"طَلَلَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTolaAlaka","text_ar":"اَطْلَالَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA $axaSa mino jasadika","text_ar":"مَا شَخَصَ مِنْ جَسَدِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God preserve,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"save, what has risen into view of thy body,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"person"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHon","text_ar":"صَحْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"court"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a house,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared for the household to sit upon:"},{"kind":"text","text":"ADk says that there was"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place on which to eat and drink in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"finaA='","text_ar":"فِنَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yard"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of every house, called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talal","text_ar":"طَلَل"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Az, TA:) accord. to ISd, (TA,) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talal","text_ar":"طَلَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a house is, or was,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of wide bench, of stone or brick"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generally built against a wall, called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duk~aAnap","text_ar":"دُكَّانَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duk~aAn","text_ar":"دُكَّان"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon which to sit."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b4-  And The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jilaAl","text_ar":"جِلَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deck"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of a ship or boat; (M, Mgh, O, K;) i. e. (Mgh) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"covering"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is like the roof"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chamber:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTolaAlN","text_ar":"اَطْلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh, Msb, TA.) [In the TA it is said to mean the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iraAE","text_ar":"شِرَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a ship or boat; which is a mistake, as is sufficiently shown by its being there immediately added, “ hence the trad. of Aboo-Bekr, that he used to pray upon the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ATlAl","text_ar":"اطلال"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the ship or boat. ”] ―         -b5-  [Hence, app.,] one says, (of a man, Ibn-'Abbád, O,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$aY EalaY Talali AlmaA='i","text_ar":"مَشَى عَلَى طَلَلِ المَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ElY","text_ar":"على"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zahorihi","text_ar":"ظَهْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ibn-'Abbád, O, K,) which, Z says, means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ElY wajohihi","text_ar":"على وَجْهِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He walked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went along, upon the surface of the water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but whether this relates to a pretended miracle or to sliding upon ice, I know not]: and he adds that it is a tropical phrase. (TA.)       -A2-  Also Anything"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fresh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"juicy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~N","text_ar":"طَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moist;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TariY~N","text_ar":"طَرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tal~N","text_ar":"طَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence."}],"source_refs":["K","S","O","Msb","TA","Az","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}